subSections.text:
{{zh-hanzi}}

# to [[do]]; to [[make]]
#* {{zh-x|見 義 不 為{wéi}，無 勇 也。|To see what is right and not to '''do it''' is want of courage.|ref=Analects}}
# {{qualifier|to turn, to transform}} [[into]]; [[to]]
#* {{zh-x|分為{wéi}|to divide into, to split into}}
#* {{zh-x|那 兩 個 組織 已 合併 為{wéi} 一 個 組織。|Those two organizations have been amalgamated '''into''' single one.}}
#* {{zh-x|它 將{jiāng} 重{chóng}新 結晶 為{wéi} 原來 的 結構。|It will recrystallize '''into''' the original structure.}}
#* {{zh-x|他 被 晉升 為{wéi} 上校。|He was promoted '''to''' colonel.}}
# to [[be]] {{qualifier|equivalent to|equal to}}
#* {{zh-x|失業率 為{wéi} @20%。|Unemployment '''is running''' at 20 per cent.}}
#* {{zh-x|它 的 寬度 為{wéi} 7 米。|It '''is''' 7 metres in width.}}
#* {{zh-x|一 公斤 為{wéi} 兩 磅。|A kilogram '''is''' two pounds.}}
# to take something as
# to [[act]] as; to [[serve]] as; to [[behave]] as
#* {{zh-x|其 竹節 度{duó} 三 尺，柔細 可 為{wéi} 索，亦 以 皮 為{wéi} 麻。|Each joint measures three ''chi''; thin and supple, it may be '''used as''' a rope, and its skin may also be '''used as''' linen.|CL|ref={{RQ:Manshu|7|Tea, Trees, Herbs and Fruits|7}}}}
# [[as]] (in the [[capacity]] of)

{{zh-hanzi}}

# [[for]]; [[to]]
#* {{zh-x|我 能 為 你 做 點 什麼 嗎？|What can I do '''for''' you?}}
#* {{zh-x|我 真 為 你 高興！|I am really happy '''for''' you!}}
#* {{zh-x|他 為 自己 的 錯誤 道歉。|He gave an apology '''for''' his mistake.}}
# [[because of]]
#: {{zh-x|你 為 這 生氣 哦{o}。|So that's what you're upset about?}}
# [[for the sake of]]
#: {{zh-x|不.為.五.斗.米.折腰|don't bow down '''for the sake of''' five pecks (or decalitres) of rice}}
